oc"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E5%8F%8A%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3"><span class="toc-number">1.</span> <span class="toc-text">基础及思想</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AE%B5%E5%8F%A5%E5%9E%8B%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93"><span class="toc-number">2.</span> <span class="toc-text">第三段句型总结</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95"><span class="toc-number">2.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">我的看法</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E"><span class="toc-number">2.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">我们怎么办</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B"><span class="toc-number">2.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">我的展望</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%B0%86%E6%9D%A5%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%A2%AB%E5%8A%A8%E8%AF%AD%E6%80%81"><span class="toc-number">2.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">一般将来时的被动语态</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E9%BB%98%E5%86%99"><span class="toc-number">2.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">默写</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%9A"><span class="toc-number">3.</span> <span class="toc-text">作业</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%F0%9F%A4%94%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%88%E5%AE%9A-%E5%A4%9A-%E6%8C%91-%E4%BF%AE-%E8%BF%9E%EF%BC%89"><span class="toc-number">3.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">🤔思路（定-多-挑-修-连）</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95-%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B"><span class="toc-number">3.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">我的看法+我们怎么办+我的展望</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95-%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E"><span class="toc-number">3.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">我的看法+我们怎么办</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B"><span class="toc-number">3.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">我的看法+我的展望</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B"><span class="toc-number">3.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">我们怎么办+我的展望</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E8%AF%8D"><span class="toc-number">3.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">连接词</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></div></div></div></div></main><footer id="footer" style="background-image: url('/img/18lian.png')"><div id="footer-wrap"><div class="copyright">&copy;2018 - 2024 By Rui's</div><div class="footer_custom_text">Hi, welcome to my <a href="https://ruilearning.github.io/">blog</a>!</div></div></footer></div><div id="rightside"><div id="rightside-config-hide"><button id="readmode" type="button" title="阅读模式"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></button><button id="translateLink" type="button" title="简繁转换">繁</button><button id="darkmode" type="button" title="浅色和深色模式转换"><i class="fas fa-adjust"></i></button><button id="hide-aside-btn" type="button" title="单栏和双栏切换"><i class="fas fa-arrows-alt-h"></i></button></div><div id="rightside-config-show"><button id="rightside_config" type="button" title="设置"><i class="fas fa-cog fa-spin"></i></button><button class="close" id="mobile-toc-button" type="button" title="目录"><i class="fas fa-list-ul"></i></button><a id="to_comment" href="#post-comment" title="直达评论"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i></a><button id="go-up" type="button" title="回到顶